title: TK6 Bar and Grill
typeOfFood: Lacto, American, Western, Fast food, Beer/Wine, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. A place to go out with friends to drink and grab a bite. Mostly fast food on the menu, a few choices for vegetarians. Has salads, a vegetarian taco, quesedilla, and burrito - be sure to order without sour cream or cheese. Located centrally in Susukino on the famous Tanuki street and frequented by foreigners. Free Wi-Fi.
streetAddress: 6-5-3 Minami 2 - Jo, Chuo-ku, Jonishi SapporoChuo Ward
